Package com.github.webapp_minifier.options

Provides options for the plugin.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DirectiveHandler
    Implementations of the DirectiveHandler receive notification of a directive in configuration and react to it.
    InlineConfigurationHandler  
    OverridablePluginOptions
    This interface defines the plugin options that can be overridable.
    PluginOptions
    This class packages the options for the plugin such that they can be easily shared between classes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultInlineConfigurationHandler
    An OptionHandler handles individually parsed options.
    DefaultOverridablePluginOptions
    This class is the default implementation of the OverridablePluginOptions interface.
    OptionsParser
    This class parses plugin options from input.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    JavaScriptCompressor
    The JavaScript Compressor types.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ParseOptionException
    This exception indicates a problem while parsing the plugin options.
